Grimlock held up his fist, and it glowed with power. "Yes. Me Grimlock
should rule. Dinobots should be Seconds in command, but we wait, until
Pacifix's peaceful ways proven wrong. This war, not some daycare." he
said, as he walked towards Pacifix and Ironhide. He didnt need any of
them, just the Dinobots, they could stop anything.
